<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar", { page: "/" }) %>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-10">
        <div class="hero bg-base-200 py-10 text-center">
            <div class="hero-content flex-col">
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Welcome</h1>
                <p class="py-4">Browse our current collection of modern solutions to help fight Climate Change.</p>
                <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3 Project Cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-10">
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/farmland.jpg" alt="Farmland" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
                    <p>Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity and sequester carbon in the process.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/cement.jpg" alt="Cement" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
                    <p>Reformulated cement reduces emissions by utilizing low-carbon binding agents and materials.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
                <figure><img src="/images/biomass.jpg" alt="Biomass" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" /></figure>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Biomass Energy</h2>
                    <p>Biomass provides renewable energy from organic materials, reducing reliance on fossil fuels.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
